        public static void convertInterfaceRealizations(java.util.ArrayList<InterfaceRealization> realizations,
                                                TemporaryModel tmpModel,
                                                Node parentNode)
        Static method converting the InterfaceRealizations of a PackagedElement to a TemporaryRelationship with references to the contract and the element itself
        Parameters:
        realizations - the list of InterfaceRealizations which should be converted
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel to which the converted TemporaryRelationship should be added
        parentNode - the Node representing the {uml.UmlModel} or UmlPackage to which the converted TemporaryRelationship should be added

        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel to which the converted TemporaryRelationships should be added
